title: AskLighter
---
<<if $torchQuestStarted == false || $torchQuestCompleted == true || $haveLighter == true>>
        Me : Hi.
<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Masked Figure 1">>
        Masked Figure : Bazingga!
        Masked Figure : Zing!
        Masked Figure : Bazooms!
<<else>>
Me : Hey, can I borrow your lighter?
Me : I need to light some torches in the forest.
Me : Your friend said you might have one.

<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Masked Figure 1">>

Masked Figure : Lighter?

<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Player">>
Me: Right.
<<wait 0.2>>

Masked Figure : Oh.
Masked Figure : I thought you said ladder.

<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Player">>
Me: Uhh... 
<<wait 0.3>>
Me: Ladder?
<<wait 0.3>>

Masked Figure : Forest is big.
Masked Figure : Torches are… smaller.

<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Player">>
Me: What?

<<wait 0.3>>

<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Masked Figure 1">>
Masked Figure : Fire goes up.
Masked Figure : Smoke goes wherever it wants.
<<wait 0.2>>
<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Player">>
Me: Uhh.. Sure?

<<wait 0.4>>

<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Masked Figure 1">>
Masked Figure : I don’t like the click sound.
Masked Figure : But it works.

<<wait 0.3>>

Masked Figure : Hold on.

<<wait 0.4>>

Masked Figure : Take this one.

<<wait 0.2>>
<<set $haveLighter = true>>
<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Masked Figure 1">>
Masked Figure : Here.
Masked Figure : Don’t shake it.
Masked Figure : Or shake it.
Masked Figure : I don’t know.

<<wait 0.1>>
<<ChangeLookAtTarget NarrationInteraction "Player">>
Me: What a weird guy.
<<endif>>
===

